<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="W" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Waftage" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Waftage,</orth> passage by water: <cit><quote>a ship you sent me to, to hire w.</quote> <bibl n="shak. err 4.1.95" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. IV, 1, 95</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>a strange soul upon the Stygian banks staying for w.</quote> <bibl n="shak. tro 3.2.11" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. III, 2, 11</bibl></cit>.
